<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-885] DefaultProducerTemplate.extractResultBody() should throw an exception if there was a failure rather than returning the input message</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-885</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;we should throw an exception if there was a Fault or the exchange contains an Exception&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12485660">CAMEL-885</key>
            <summary>DefaultProducerTemplate.extractResultBody() should throw an exception if there was a failure rather than returning the input message</summary>
